====================
    Genera Fonts
====================
CLFSWM uses `bfd` format Symbolics Genera fonts in the git submodule
`genera-fonts`. The default font is `genera-cptfontc`.

Installation
============
To install fonts, first create a directory `/usr/share/fonts/genera`,
and copying all files under `genera-fonts/bfd` to it, then make
X Window recognize these fonts by adding these two lines to `.xintrc`.

    xset fp+ ~/x11/fonts/genera/
    xset fp rehash


